 A tiny library for building parameterized URLs. It is intended to be used
with records to give the parameters names and therefore reducing errors.

    userUrl : Url { id : Int }
    userUrl = root </> s "users" </> int .id

    userUrl @ { id = 42 } == "/users/42"


